string-array.name: welcome_line2_array
string-array.item: Welcome to the world of Pokemon!
People call me the Pokemon Prof!
Now tell me. Are you a boy? Or are you a girl?
This world is inhabited far and wide by creatures called Pokemon.
Now, PLAYER, which Pokemon do you want?
A world of dreams and adventures with Pokemon awaits! Let\'s go!

string-array.name: welcome_line1_array
string-array.item: First, tell me a little about yourself.
Right... So you are PLAYER from HOMETOWN!
I have 3 Pokemon here, but you can have one!
Your very own Pokemon legend is about to unfold!
